- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses estimation of parameters from data. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses the effective sample size and sub-Gaussian structure. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with distributed networks and centralized processing. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses estimation of parameters from independent samples.
